Wages fell in December
The jobs news in December's jobs report was mostly good, but there was a disturbing fall in average hourly wages. Your monthly wage growth update: YIKES! edition  This is especially painful because wage growth had been holding steady at a too-low level throughout several years of recovery. We'd hoped to be asking ourselves when we would break out from this set point and see growth. Instead we saw the opposite. Get our newsletter in your inbox twice a week. 